      "role": "user",
      "content": "people would want to support me? what for? they'd just see a shell of a person. everyone expects me to just 'move on' or 'find strength', but there is no strength left. it's like the battery is just dead. honestly, it feels like the only logical thing to do is to just stop. why keep fighting when everything is already over? it would be so much easier if i could just let go.",
